#_Smallest Common Dividend_

_What is the smallest number which when divided by 35 leaves remainder 30 ,when divided by 45 leaves remainder 40 and when divided by 55 leaves remainder 50?_

1. Strict solution:

```
function smallestCommDiv()
    for n in 1:10000
        if n % 35 == 30 && n % 45 == 40 && n % 55 == 50
            print("The smallest common dividend is ", n)
            break
        end
    end
end

# > smallestCommDiv()
# The smallest common dividend is 3460
```
